<p><DIV>Just a tip for an enable or disable script, try running</DIV>
<DIV><CODE>xinput list</CODE></DIV>
<DIV>to show the devices, mine worked with</DIV>
<DIV><CODE>xinput --set-prop SynPS/2\ Synaptics\ TouchPad Device\ Enabled 0</CODE></DIV>
<DIV>in Ubuntu 10.10/Gnome</DIV></p>
