<p><p>If you're running Gnome (on Fedora 14)<br></p><p>1. System-&gt;Preferences-&gt;Mouse</p><p>2. Go to Touchpad tab</p><p>3. Select ' Disable touchpad while typing'<br></p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>
