<div id="comment13472" class="commentContainer commentLevel0">
<p><p>also need to launch the xhost application (requires /root/.Xauthority to exist...can be a sym link to your primary user directory file)<br></p><p>to turn off is now:</p><p>&nbsp;sh -c 'export DISPLAY=:0; export PROTOCOL=auto-dev; export XAUTHORITY=/root/.Xauthority; /usr/bin/xhost +localhost; /usr/bin/xinput --set-prop "SynPS/2 Synaptics TouchPad" "Device Enabled" 0' &gt;&gt;/var/log/synoff 2&gt;&gt;/var/log/synoff</p></p>
</div>
